he labor movement in the late 1800s and early 1900s.<br /><i><u>Date Adopted or Revised</u></i>: 05/23<br /></td>    </tr> </table></td></tr></table>     </td></tr></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="#000000"><tr><td width="25%" align="center" Valign="top"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: Arial">SS.912.A.3.10</span></td><td width="75%"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: Arial">Review different economic and philosophic ideologies.</span><table align="center" border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse;width:100%;font-family: Arial;font-size: 9.0pt;" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="#000000"> <tr colpsan="2" style="width:100%;font-family: Arial"><td style="width:100%;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;">Related Access Point(s)</td></tr> <tr>      <td> SS.912.A.3.AP.10<br>Compare major differences in economic and philosophic ideologies.<br /><i><u>Date Adopted or Revised</u></i>: 05/23<br /></td>    </tr> </table></td></tr></table>     </td></tr></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="#000000"><tr><td width="25%" align="center" Valign="top"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: Arial">SS.912.A.3.11</span></td><td width="75%"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: Arial">Analyze the impact of political machines in United States cities in the late 19th and early 20th centuries.</span><table align="center" border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse;width:100%;font-family: Arial;font-size: 9.0pt;" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="#000000"> <tr colpsan="2" style="width:100%;font-family: Arial"><td style="width:100%;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;">Related Access Point(s)</td></tr> <tr>      <td> SS.912.A.3.AP.11<br>Identify ways powerful groups (political machines) in United States cities controlled the government in the late 18