> 7: </asp:Label><asp:Label Font-Bold="true" ID="Label5" runat="server">Understand the rise and continuing international influence of the United States as a world leader and the impact of contemporary social and political movements on American life.</asp:Label><br /><br /><div><asp:Label ID="Label6" Font-Italic="true" runat="server"></asp:Label></div></span></td></tr></table></div><table align="center" width="100%" border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="black"><tr><td bordercolor="black" width="25%" align="center" bgcolor="#CCCCCC"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: Arial"><b>BENCHMARK CODE</b></span></td><td bordercolor="black" width="75%" align="center" bgcolor="#CCCCCC"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: Arial"><b>BENCHMARK</b></span></td></tr></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="#000000"><tr><td width="25%" align="center" Valign="top"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: Arial">SS.912.A.7.1</span></td><td width="75%"><span style="font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: Arial">Identify causes for Post-World War II prosperity and its effects on American society.</span><table align="center" border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse;width:100%;font-family: Arial;font-size: 9.0pt;" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="#000000"> <tr colpsan="2" style="width:100%;font-family: Arial"><td style="width:100%;text-align:center;font-weight:bold;">Related Access Point(s)</td></tr> <tr>      <td> SS.912.A.7.AP.1<br>Identify a cause and effect of post-World War II prosperity on American society.<br /><i><u>Date Adopted or Revised</u></i>: 05/23<br /></td>    </tr> </table></td></tr></table>     </td></tr></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="#000000"><tr><td width="25%" align="center" Valign="top"><span style="font